ALTER TABLE `item_template` DROP PRIMARY KEY,  ADD PRIMARY KEY (entry,patch);
ALTER TABLE item_template ADD COLUMN patch tinyint(3) DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL AFTER entry;

CREATE TABLE `forbidden_items` (
  `entry` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `patch` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `AfterOrBefore` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`entry`,`AfterOrBefore`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
 

 PRIMARY KEY (`entry`,`patch`)
